        <generalfeedback format="html">
            <text><![CDATA[
<ul>
    <li>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            The modulus of \(x\) is defined as \[|x|=\begin{cases} x &amp; \text{if } x&gt;0 \\ -x &amp; \text{if } x&lt;0 \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Absoluttverdien til \(x\) er definert som \[|x|=\begin{cases} x &amp; \text{hvis } x&gt;0 \\ -x &amp; \text{hvis } x&lt;0 \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Therefore, if \(|x|&gt;0\) then \(x&gt;0\)
            <i>
                <b>
                    or
                </b>
            </i>
            \(x&lt;0\) - clearly both cases cannot occur at the same time.
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Derfor, hvis \(|x|&gt;0\) s&#229; er \(x&gt;0\)
            <i>
                <b>
                    eller
                </b>
            </i>
            \(x&lt;0\) &#8211; s&#229; klart kan ikke begge tilfellene oppst&#229; samtidig.
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Similarly, if \(|x|&lt;0\) then \(x&gt;0\)
            <i>
                <b>
                    or
                </b>
            </i>
            \(x&lt;0\).
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Tilsvarende, hvis \(|x|&lt;0\) s&#229; er \(x&gt;0\)
            <i>
                <b>
                    eller
                </b>
            </i>
            \(x&lt;0\).
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            The modulus of \(x\) minus an arbitrary constant \(a\) is defined as \[ |x-a| = \begin{cases} x-a &amp; \text{if } x&gt;a \\ a-x &amp; \text{if } x&lt;a \\ 0 &amp; \text{if } x=a \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Absoluttverdien til \(x\) minus en vilk&#229;rlig konstant \(a\) er definert som \[ |x-a| = \begin{cases} x-a &amp; \text{hvis } x&gt;a \\ a-x &amp; \text{hvis } x&lt;a \\ 0 &amp; \text{hvis } x=a \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Therefore, if \(|x-a|&lt;b\), then \(x-a&lt;b\)
            <b>
                <i>
                    and
                </i>
            </b>
            \(a-x&lt;b\).
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Derfor, hvis \(|x-a|&lt;b\), s&#229; er \(x-a&lt;b\)
            <b>
                <i>
                    og
                </i>
            </b>
            \(a-x&lt;b\).
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            The modulus of \(x\) plus an arbitrary constant \(a\) is defined as \[ |x+a| = \begin{cases} x+a &amp; \text{if } x+a&gt;0 \\ -x-a &amp; \text{if } x+a&lt;0 \\ 0 &amp; \text{if } x=-a \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Absoluttverdien til \(x\) pluss en vilk&#229;rlig konstant \(a\) er definert som \[ |x+a| = \begin{cases} x+a &amp; \text{hvis } x+a&gt;0 \\ -x-a &amp; \text{hvis } x+a&lt;0 \\ 0 &amp; \text{hvis } x=-a \end{cases}, \]
        </span>
        <p>
        </p>
        <span class="multilang" lang="en">
            Therefore, if \(|x+a|&lt;b\), then \(x+a&lt;b\)
            <b>
                <i>
                    and
                </i>
            </b>
            \(-x-a&lt;b\).
        </span>
        <span class="multilang" lang="no">
            Derfor, hvis \(|x+a|&lt;b\), s&#229; er \(x+a&lt;b\)
            <b>
                <i>
                    og
                </i>
            </b>
            \(-x-a&lt;b\).
        </span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
</p>
]]></text>
